<h1>About {{ site.title }}</h1>
<p>We believe perfume is deeply personal, yet universal in its power to transport and transform. Our reviews go beyond pyramid breakdowns to explore how fragrances actually wear throughout the day, their emotional resonance, and their honest value. We test everything on real skin, in real life, because a scent's true character only reveals itself over time. Whether you're seeking your signature or simply curious, we help you navigate the world of fragrance with clarity and genuine enthusiasm.</p>
<p style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px;">
Reviews on this site synthesize publicly available research and reflect one perspective on each product.
Scoring categories and weights are chosen per product to fit what matters for that item.
</p>
